a terrible thing.

22:01.529 --> 22:02.689
This should be good.

22:02.780 --> 22:07.149
| used my ability
to push one man's memories
into another man's head.

22:07.243 --> 22:08.779
Yeah, my head.

22:08.870 --> 22:12.203
