23:21.985 --> 23:25.398
SYLAR: (SIGHS)
That was pretty smart,
even for you,

23:25.488 --> 23:27.820
not letting her tell me
where she's gonna be.

23:28.825 --> 23:32.909
But you still haven't
figured out how to
get rid of me, genius.

23:34.497 --> 23:36.783
(LAUGHS)

23:40.336 --> 23:42.042
Mohinder, look,
I have no idea
where you are.

23:42.130 --> 23:43.461
Just... Will you
do me a favor?

23:43.548 --> 23:47.712
