what I can do?

26:03.479 --> 26:06.221
You'll learn to
control your ability
with Tracy's help.

26:06.649 --> 26:09.982
But you're gonna
keep it to yourself.
It's the only way.

26:10.820 --> 26:12.435
What if something happens?

26:15.408 --> 26:18.445
Nothing's going to happen.
You'll be safe.

26:22.081 --> 26:23.992
You'll be invisible.

26:30.590 --> 26:33.923
GRETCHEN: So, what,
you think a sorority brought
us out here to kill us?

26:34.010 --> 26:36.501
That's ridiculous.
It's just a game.

26:36.596 --> 26:38.427
CLAIRE: It didn't
just move itself.

26:39.098 --> 26:40.759
But there was
no one else there.

26:40.850 --> 26:43.262
How else would you
explain it?

26:43.352 --> 26:45.604
In my world,
there's a million ways.

26:45.688 --> 26:47.098
Name one.

26:47.190 --> 26:48.350
Telekinesis.

26:49.192 --> 26:52.355
I've seen it.
Heck, I know
someone who has it.

26:52.987 --> 26:56.730
So, wait, you're saying
there's another
one of you here?

26:56.824 --> 26:58.655
CLAIRE: It's very possible.

26:59.285 --> 27:02.072
And, what, they're bored
and they're playing
a college prank on you?

27:03.331 --> 27:04.787
Not a prank.

27:05.708 --> 27:08.541
You think that
they're trying
to kill you?

27:09.212 --> 27:10.497
Not me.

27:10.588 --> 27:11.623
