27:16.052 --> 27:18.714
Me? Come on.

27:18.805 --> 27:22.423
Think about it.
My first roommate
committed suicide

27:22.517 --> 27:26.385
with a mysterious note
that wasn't there,
but then it was.

27:26.479 --> 27:29.721
I mean, maybe
you almost getting gutted
wasn't a coincidence.

27:30.900 --> 27:33.812
Claire, that is
a little out there.

27:33.903 --> 27:36.861
Sounds like some
crazy-ass conspiracy theory.

27:39.200 --> 27:41.407
Which pretty much
describes your entire life.

27:44.413 --> 27:45.914
What was that?

27:48.292 --> 27:49.748
I don't know.

27:51.254 --> 27:52.243
(ASHLEY PANTING)

27:52.338 --> 27:53.544
(SCREAMING)

27:54.173 --> 27:55.379
Ash, cut it out.
Come on.

27:56.384 --> 27:58.625
Hey, you guys
all right?

27:58.761 --> 27:59.796
You find another clue?

27:59.887 --> 28:01.172
Like I'm gonna
tell you.

28:02.056 --> 28:03.512
Look, your roommate's
freaked out,

28:03.599 --> 28:05.385
and we don't care
about the treasure.

28:05.476 --> 28:07.512
Let's just stick together,
get the hell out of here,

28:07.603 --> 28:10.515
and once we find it,
you can have it. Deal?

28:11.065 --> 28:13.727
Okay. Can we just go?
Deal.

28:15.111 --> 28:16.476
Lead the way.

28:38.885 --> 28:40.796
(PEOPLE CLAMORING)

28:54.066 --> 28:56.102
MR. BENNET:
Take my car.
Straight ahead.

28:56.944 --> 28:57.933
WOMAN: You're sick!

28:58.029 --> 29:00.270
MAN: We know what happened
to your parents!

29:04.744 --> 29:08.032
Hey, you're getting away
with murder, you...
Let go of him.

29:08.122 --> 29:09.157
Hey.

29:09.248 --> 29:10.749
TRACY: Don't hurt him.

29:10.833 --> 29:12.949
MR. BENNET:
Jeremy, stop. Let him go.

29:15.379 --> 29:17.119
(MAN GROANS)

29:20.509 --> 29:21.715
Get the hell
away from him.

29:21.844 --> 29:25.257
Jeremy. Jeremy.
Jeremy, you can save him.
Get the hell away from him.

29:25.348 --> 29:26.679
Everyone, back. Back.

29:26.766 --> 29:29.508
Jeremy, listen to me.
You can help him.
You can save him.

29:29.602 --> 29:30.967
Everybody, stand back.

29:31.062 --> 29:33.223
(ECHOING)
Now, listen, son.

29:33.314 --> 29:35.054
You're going back in there,
