29:36.150 --> 29:39.108
You know what you did
to your momma and your daddy.

29:40.321 --> 29:43.063
Jeremy, come on.
You can save him.
You can do it.

29:50.998 --> 29:52.283
Jeremy.

30:06.889 --> 30:10.177
You do not understand
the first thing about
what's happening here.

30:10.267 --> 30:12.929
Three people are dead.
I understand that.

30:13.020 --> 30:15.682
And that boy,
whatever he is,
is responsible.

30:15.773 --> 30:19.391
Hey, do you want it
to happen again?
Just let me talk to him.

30:20.695 --> 30:22.185
Talk to him?

30:23.155 --> 30:26.488
You're through
talking to him.
Both of you.

30:34.458 --> 30:37.825
You think
killers go free, huh?
Not in this town.

30:44.343 --> 30:46.254
Gil, where's the boy?

30:49.306 --> 30:50.716
Gil, do you read?

30:51.100 --> 30:55.935
The boy is gone.
