(GROANS)

31:24.759 --> 31:26.295
(SOBS)

31:30.306 --> 31:31.591
You're not normal.

31:31.724 --> 31:33.760
(LAUGHS)
You don't belong here.

31:39.315 --> 31:40.395
Go.

31:44.528 --> 31:46.064
(MATT GROANS)

31:47.156 --> 31:48.487
You like that?

31:49.325 --> 31:50.861
You know what this is?

31:51.452 --> 31:56.822
I bought this with Janice
on our anniversary trip
to Ensenada.

31:57.458 --> 32:01.201
And it is so poetic
that I'm using it
to bury you.

32:01.295 --> 32:03.581
Bury me
or drown the truth?

32:03.672 --> 32:06.414
The truth? What?
That you're nothing.

32:06.509 --> 32:08.625
You're just a figment
of my imagination.

32:09.095 --> 32:10.380
(GROANS)

32:10.471 --> 32:12.837
Let's quiet those voices,
shall we?

32:16.644 --> 32:18.760
Your wife
walked out on you.

32:20.356 --> 32:22.722
You think she wanted
to give you your space?

32:22.817 --> 32:26.059
She can't stand
the sight of you.
You're pathetic.

32:26.153 --> 32:30.522
You know what
she said to me in front
