36:19.511 --> 36:21.012
Stop! Stop!

36:21.096 --> 36:22.427
OLIVIA: Don't! Don't...

36:23.223 --> 36:25.214
What the...
ASHLEY: What?

36:25.309 --> 36:26.924
OLIVIA: How did you...

36:28.437 --> 36:30.177
