saved him.

37:23.325 --> 37:25.236
He needed a home.

37:29.915 --> 37:31.451
A real home.

37:46.849 --> 37:48.259
Tracy.

37:49.184 --> 37:50.344
Hey.

37:51.186 --> 37:52.847
Tracy, I'm sorry.

37:54.982 --> 37:57.143
You know,
this was supposed
to be simple.

37:57.234 --> 37:58.895
Just go in
and sign him out.

38:00.028 --> 38:01.279
