all these years.

38:22.885 --> 38:24.967
Do we have
to be invisible?

38:25.345 --> 38:28.257
You ever think
we could just live, Noah?

38:28.348 --> 38:29.929
Out in the open?

38:33.061 --> 38:34.722
After today, no.

38:37.274 --> 38:39.230
