39:06.136 --> 39:07.592
(SNIFFS)

39:15.437 --> 39:16.938
(GRUNTS)

39:21.360 --> 39:22.440
Hi.

39:22.528 --> 39:23.768
Hey.

39:26.281 --> 39:28.772
You gave us
quite a scare
there, brother.

39:31.036 --> 39:33.152
I know. I'm sorry.
ljust...

39:34.957 --> 39:39.200
I had to see if I could...

39:42.589 --> 39:44.545
