You hear me?

39:56.728 --> 39:57.979
Yeah.

39:59.147 --> 40:01.183
Thanks. Both of you.

40:05.279 --> 40:06.485
I love you.

40:06.572 --> 40:08.062
(LAUGHS)

40:08.156 --> 40:10.738
